{"tid":1403260,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[推比前線知]如何對抗速龍","createTime":"2019-08-03T18:11:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T10:57:04.000Z","uid":5290,"like":194,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"6f31ff4889db1388746f4b890b6df1747cba3df4","tid":1403260,"uid":5290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:11:52.000Z","msg":"就係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">磚雨！！！</span></span><br />\n次次速龍衝埋嚟<br />\n理得你後面幾萬人<br />\n明明可以十圍一都淆底<br />\n但淆底係絕對正常<br />\n我見到都好撚淆<br />\n但對面同我地一樣係血肉之軀<br />\n一樣會淆<br />\n<br />\n話說Winter on fire<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當中有一段係<br />\n前線有一位示威者掟磚<br />\n軍隊衝上嚟捉人<br />\n即刻一百幾十粒磚車埋去<br />\n前線即刻去救返佢<br />\n<br />\n點解次次對家都要派人<br />\n痴膠水痴撚實哂D磚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為對面真係好撚驚你地掉磚囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔該各位以後係前線<br />\n放滿哂磚係地下<br />\n磚要碎成細舊<br />\n方便一手拎起掉<br />\n同埋最好就起撚哂角<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家記住戴返隻手套<br />\n唔好整親隻手仔<br />\n<br />\n第一排揸盾<br />\n第二排做遠攻<br />\n第三排先做滅煙/旗手<br />\n（無煙滅就幫手掉）<br />\n太後就唔好掉啦<br />\n以防tk隊友<br />\n但可以幫手傳磚上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一有速龍衝埋嚟就一百幾十粒車埋去<br />\n我就唔信磚雨對面都唔淆照衝埋嚟<br />\n就當有少數速龍真係唔淆<br />\n但衝過嚟嘅速龍就會變少<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個時候真係夠薑嘅勇武就可以上前圍佢<br />\n如果佢地退<br />\n可以上前執起地下之前拋出嘅磚追擊<br />\n<br />\n太大煙咩都睇唔到照樣一百幾十粒車埋去<br />\n掩護手足撤退<br />\n以防有狗衝埋嚟<br />\n<br />\n另外搬運方面<br />\n除左用有轆垃圾桶外<br />\n發夢見到手足起左太多<br />\n放落紅白藍膠袋搬唔到<br />\n因為太多個袋會穿<br />\n可以的話分多幾次搬<br />\n<br />\n當然<br />\n希望有一日見到<br />\n磚雨會升級做魔法攻擊<br />\n請班狗飲酒<br />\n魔法雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以上都係發夢夢見<br />\n祝各位手足<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">武運昌隆</span></span><br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"5225f4ada5921e927a6599fbd7191c0c22210019","tid":1403260,"uid":5290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:14:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b245748df4797d0e271b274941724d2a2959c9f","tid":1403260,"uid":172626,"like":7,"dislike":53,"score":-46,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:14:42.000Z","msg":"扔磚還扔磚 最重要不忘初心 唔好將目標鎖定係仇警身上 因為我地既重點不在警察"},{"pid":"d0b5c19a1db62e08e2580d0aa06c55d02d49f739","tid":1403260,"uid":131836,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:16:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7e08221aaabaa21df6c91b3ec679fae8b922b9f","tid":1403260,"uid":263038,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:16:25.000Z","msg":"講得好<br />\n遇速龍一定要反抗<br />\n走佬嘅話只會有十幾個走唔切嘅手足被捉走<br />\n全部人一齊反抗嘅話<br />\n冇人會被人捉之餘<br />\n走佬嘅就係速龍"},{"pid":"613e12633e17669ed4637661a16752c0cdb975e3","tid":1403260,"uid":136187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:16:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5acf163819cd37b271c86d2a1d8ed8192628eee3","tid":1403260,"uid":263038,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"0b245748df4797d0e271b274941724d2a2959c9f","tid":1403260,"uid":172626,"like":7,"dislike":53,"score":-46,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:14:42.000Z","msg":"扔磚還扔磚 最重要不忘初心 唔好將目標鎖定係仇警身上 因為我地既重點不在警察"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:17:10.000Z","msg":"仲有千奇唔好掟中記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"797df9ef9dbfb66edfa8f794e2c0fd106c250ae7","tid":1403260,"uid":263038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:17:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2ecdc46184840b3ef5879db9a021e8b8964ef72d","tid":1403260,"uid":113250,"l