2a2da1fdbf72e362f30965dbe8504e5735533","tid":1403260,"uid":7648,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:53:49.000Z","msg":"補圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p0hVikU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp0hVikU.png&h=9562225c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"22dd8c46de05b516911e3e5783421606722cd791","tid":1403260,"uid":246884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:57:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c5ff6d68aa52aada614c11350a5545340b2aadb1","tid":1403260,"uid":5290,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5872a2da1fdbf72e362f30965dbe8504e5735533","tid":1403260,"uid":7648,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:53:49.000Z","msg":"補圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p0hVikU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp0hVikU.png&h=9562225c&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:58:40.000Z","msg":"佢地企定定就蛋<br />\n佢地狗衝埋嚟一定係磚"},{"pid":"ecac89d2e2a2a6612bfeb5c9b843f9cd0fd88e58","tid":1403260,"uid":258748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f31ff4889db1388746f4b890b6df1747cba3df4","tid":1403260,"uid":5290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:11:52.000Z","msg":"就係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">磚雨！！！</span></span><br />\n次次速龍衝埋嚟<br />\n理得你後面幾萬人<br />\n明明可以十圍一都淆底<br />\n但淆底係絕對正常<br />\n我見到都好撚淆<br />\n但對面同我地一樣係血肉之軀<br />\n一樣會淆<br />\n<br />\n話說Winter on fire<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當中有一段係<br />\n前線有一位示威者掟磚<br />\n軍隊衝上嚟捉人<br />\n即刻一百幾十粒磚車埋去<br />\n前線即刻去救返佢<br />\n<br />\n點解次次對家都要派人<br />\n痴膠水痴撚實哂D磚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為對面真係好撚驚你地掉磚囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔該各位以後係前線<br />\n放滿哂磚係地下<br />\n磚要碎成細舊<br />\n方便一手拎起掉<br />\n同埋最好就起撚哂角<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家記住戴返隻手套<br />\n唔好整親隻手仔<br />\n<br />\n第一排揸盾<br />\n第二排做遠攻<br />\n第三排先做滅煙/旗手<br />\n（無煙滅就幫手掉）<br />\n太後就唔好掉啦<br />\n以防tk隊友<br />\n但可以幫手傳磚上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一有速龍衝埋嚟就一百幾十粒車埋去<br />\n我就唔信磚雨對面都唔淆照衝埋嚟<br />\n就當有少數速龍真係唔淆<br />\n但衝過嚟嘅速龍就會變少<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個時候真係夠薑嘅勇武就可以上前圍佢<br />\n如果佢地退<br />\n可以上前執起地下之前拋出嘅磚追擊<br />\n<br />\n太大煙咩都睇唔到照樣一百幾十粒車埋去<br />\n掩護手足撤退<br />\n以防有狗衝埋嚟<br />\n<br />\n另外搬運方面<br />\n除左用有轆垃圾桶外<br />\n發夢見到手足起左太多<br />\n放落紅白藍膠袋搬唔到<br />\n因為太多個袋會穿<br />\n可以的話分多幾次搬<br />\n<br />\n當然<br />\n希望有一日見到<br />\n磚雨會升級做魔法攻擊<br />\n請班狗飲酒<br />\n魔法雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以上都係發夢夢見<br />\n祝各位手足<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">武運昌隆</span></span><br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T19:12:34.000Z","msg":"丫叉加老鼠膠雨，有無得諗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又有視覺效果，中左個身會痴住Gear或者件衫，痴住佢鞋底又跑慢左"},{"pid":"4aabe3e115ebe7d80ea0fec95f56972917d5fad0","tid":1403260,"uid":163084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T19:19:43.000Z","msg":"扔佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5802c7e0a32ce7b64e76ccf4e1d60b2131200c97","tid":1403260,"uid":38692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T19:23:18.000Z","msg":"<strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong>"},{"pid":"3c7e735bff4fe677928fadf7ab545d0d2f67e1ee","tid":1403260,"uid":153258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T19:30:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f35f9c3a1ed0a1cb595115